Display Menu:
    Display "Menu"
    Display "1. Load Data Structure"
    Display "2. Print Course List"
    Display "3. Print Course"
    Display "4. Exit"

    Read user input

    If user input is "1":
        Call Load Data Structure function
    Else if user input is "2":
        Call Print Course List function
    Else if user input is "3":
        Call Print Course function
    Else if user input is "4":
        Exit program
    Else:
        Display "Invalid input. Please try again."
        Call Display Menu function again


Load Data Structure:
    Read file data into data structure

Print Course List:
    Sort course information by alphanumeric course number from lowest to highest
    Print sorted list to display

Print Course:
    Prompt user for course number
    Search data structure for course number
    If course is found:
        Print course title and prerequisites
    Else:
        Display "Course not found. Please try again."

Exit program
